name: zpizza Columbia USC
text: We love our pizza!!! Lots of healthy choices available - gluten free, vegan, wheat. Also have salads, wings (pesto, buffalo, BBQ), crispy fries, cheesy bread, meatball subs, calzones, sandwiches. Try our catering for your next event! :-)

name: Benjamin Lamm
text: Slow service for overpriced pizza. Waited 30 min for two personal pizzas - $30 total - and one was so raw I had to rebake it at home. Do yourself a favor and go the extra two blocks to Maddios.
